      <title>卢拉公布创纪录农作物融资计划以争取巴西农民支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/lula-unveils-record-crop-financing-plan-in-bid-for-farm-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦宣布提供创纪录的巨额资金来支持巴西庞大的农业部门，这是他争取广泛反对其政府的农民支持的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/lula-unveils-record-crop-financing-plan-in-bid-for-farm-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 20:24:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>非营利组织 Mark Meadows 为法律费用提供资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/mark-meadows-nonprofit-funneled-cash-for-legal-bills-group-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据周三向华盛顿特区总检察长提交的投诉，一个自由派团体指控前白宫办公厅主任马克·梅多斯的非营利性雇主向一个组织提供资金，用于在梅多斯因推翻 2020 年大选而接受调查期间支付他的法律费用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/mark-meadows-nonprofit-funneled-cash-for-legal-bills-group-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 20:18:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列收到哈马斯关于可能的人质交易的最新回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/israel-gets-latest-hamas-response-on-possible-hostage-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡的办公室表示，以色列已收到哈马斯对拟议的人质和停火协议的最新回应，调解人员继续努力达成一项可能结束加沙地带近九个月战斗的协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/israel-gets-latest-hamas-response-on-possible-hostage-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 19:34:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>多伦多席位失利引发辞职呼声 特鲁多坚持立场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/trudeau-digs-in-after-toronto-seat-loss-sparks-resignation-calls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多明确表示，尽管在多伦多特别选举中失利，使他陷入了职业生涯中最艰难的政治危机，但他仍打算继续留任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/trudeau-digs-in-after-toronto-seat-loss-sparks-resignation-calls</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 18:23:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>辩论后，纽约时报民意调查显示特朗普领先拜登</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/trump-lead-over-biden-grows-in-post-debate-new-york-times-poll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据两项著名的全国民意调查，共和党人唐纳德·特朗普对总统乔·拜登的领先优势已扩大到 6 个百分点，这加大了这位陷入困境的民主党现任总统退出的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/trump-lead-over-biden-grows-in-post-debate-new-york-times-poll</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 17:56:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选消息不断升温，华尔街警惕拜登退场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/wall-street-on-alert-for-biden-exit-as-trump-win-trades-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华盛顿关于总统乔·拜登是否放弃竞选连任的激烈辩论正在蔓延到华尔街，交易员们正在将资金转移到美元、美国国债和其他可能受唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫影响的资产上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/wall-street-on-alert-for-biden-exit-as-trump-win-trades-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 17:53:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>白宫宣布向乌克兰提供 23 亿美元武器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/white-house-to-announce-2-3-billion-package-of-arms-for-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据美国官员透露，白宫宣布向乌克兰提供价值 23 亿美元的武器装备，其中包括五角大楼库存的设备以及与洛克希德马丁公司和 RTX 公司签订的防空武器长期合同。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/white-house-to-announce-2-3-billion-package-of-arms-for-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 17:40:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽森废除犯罪法案，震惊加州政坛</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/newsom-shocks-california-politics-by-scrapping-crime-measure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州州长加文·纽瑟姆 (Gavin Newsom) 突然放弃了一项经过精心谈判、旨在解决财产犯罪和芬太尼危机的投票措施，令该州政界感到震惊，而就在此前一天，州长办公室刚刚大肆宣扬了这项提议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/newsom-shocks-california-politics-by-scrapping-crime-measure</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 15:40:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登难以抑制退出竞选的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/biden-faces-mounting-pressure-as-report-says-he-is-weighing-exit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，《纽约时报》刊登了一篇爆炸性报道称，拜登总统已将退出总统竞选的可能性承认给一位关键盟友，而民主党内部也出现了要求他退出的运动，这进一步加剧了要求拜登总统退出总统竞选的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/biden-faces-mounting-pressure-as-report-says-he-is-weighing-exit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 15:26:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民主党人心中的问题：如何取代拜登？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/democrats-question-replacing-biden-here-s-how-it-could-work</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登在辩论中的表现令人担忧地糟糕，这引发了新的疑问：民主党是否还有其他选择，只能保留这位 81 岁的现任总统作为 11 月总统大选的候选人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/democrats-question-replacing-biden-here-s-how-it-could-work</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 05:42:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
